    </header>
    <p data-aid="158176688" id="aside3_p1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0.778em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; color: rgb(83, 87, 91); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; --height: 75.5625px;">背教についてどのくらい詳細に教えるかは，相手の必要と背景に合わせてください。イエス・キリストの福音が回復される必要があったことが理解できるように助けましょう。</p>
    <section style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Serif&quot;, McKay, &quot;McKay ldsLat&quot;, Palatino, &quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;, Palatino-Roman, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; clear: left; overflow: auto; color: rgb(83, 87, 91); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">
      <header style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.778em 0px 0.444em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;">
        <p class="title" data-aid="158176695" id="aside3_title2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif-medium, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; color: var(--text-secondary, var(--grey40)); --height: 25.1875px;">教えるとよい重要な点</p>
      </header>
      <ul class="bullet" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.3em; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0.778em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none disc; display: block;">
        <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.222em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: list-item;">
          <p data-aid="158176702" id="aside3_p2" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; --height: 125.9375px;">ほとんどの人々がイエス・キリストと主の使徒たちを拒みました（<a
              class="scripture-ref" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/nt/matt/24.9?lang=jpn#p9"
              style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-link, var(--info40)); text-decoration: none;">マタイ24：9</a>；<a
              class="scripture-ref" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.32-34?lang=jpn#p32"
              style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-link, var(--info40)); text-decoration: none;">1ニーファイ11：32－34</a>；<a
              class="scripture-ref" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.5?lang=jpn#p5"
              style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-link, var(--info40)); text-decoration: none;">2ニーファイ27：5</a>参照）。使徒たちの死後，地上から神権が失われました。バプテスマを施したり，教会を導いたりする権能はもはや存在しませんでした。</p>
        </li>
        <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.222em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: list-item;">
          <p data-aid="158176709" id="aside3_p3" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; --height: 176.3125px;">最初クリスチャンを迫害していたローマ帝国は，後にキリスト教を取り入れました。宗教に関する重要な質問は，神からの啓示ではなく，評議会での論議によって解決されました。教義と儀式は論議の対象となり，この世の考えに沿うものへと変えられていきました。これらの論議での決定に基づいて，信条や信仰の声明が作られました（<a
              class="scripture-ref" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.19?lang=jpn#p19"
              style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-link, var(--info40)); text-decoration: none;">ジョセフ・スミス—歴史1：19</a>参照）。</p>
        </li>
        <li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.222em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: list-item;">
          <p data-aid="158176716" id="aside3_p4" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; --height: 100.75px;">存在しているものを修正することによってキリスト教を改革しようとする人々もいました。しかし，神の神権の権能が地上になかったため，イエス・キリストの教会を再び設立するには権能と真理の回復が必要でした。</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
